data.description: A charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence nestled in the heart of McAllen. Situated on a fantastic corner lot, this home boasts a generous backyard and a covered patio, perfect for hosting guests and family BBQs. It is conveniently located in a terrific school district, with numerous excellent dining and shopping choices in close proximity. Priced attractively for a quick move!
